msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:845.1"
msgid "應與求罪自性毘奈耶　當與求罪自性毘奈耶"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="as5" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:846.1"
msgid "adhikaraṇasamatha 5"
msgstr "adhikaraṇasamatha 5"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:847.1"
msgid "應與多人語毘奈耶　當與多人語毘奈耶"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="as6" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:848.1"
msgid "adhikaraṇasamatha 6"
msgstr "adhikaraṇasamatha 6"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:849.1"
msgid "應與自言毘奈耶　當與自言毘奈耶"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="as7" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:850.1"
msgid "adhikaraṇasamatha 7"
msgstr "adhikaraṇasamatha 7"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:851.1"
msgid "應與草掩毘奈耶　當與草掩毘奈耶"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:852.1"
msgid "若有諍事起。當以七法順大師教。如法如律而除滅之。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:853.1"
msgid "諸大德。我已說七滅諍法。今問。諸大德。是中清淨不<span class=\"t-note\">(如是三說)</span>。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:854.1"
msgid "諸大德。是中清淨默然故。我今如是持。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
#. <span class="add"><a id="conc" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:855.1"
msgid "Conclusion"
msgstr "Conclusion"

#. </a></span>
#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="63"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:856.1"
msgid "諸大德。我已說戒經序已說八波羅市迦法。二十僧伽伐尸沙法。三十三泥薩祇波逸底迦法。一百八十波逸底迦法。十一波羅底提舍尼法眾學法。七滅諍法。此是如來應正等覺戒經中所說所攝。若更有餘法之隨法。與此相應者。皆當修學。仁等共集歡喜無諍。一心一說如水乳合。慇懃光顯大師聖教。令安樂住。勿為放逸。應當修學。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
#. <span class="add"><a id="conc-verses" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:857.1"
msgid "Concluding verses"
msgstr "Concluding verses"

#. </a></span>
#. </h2><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:858.1"
msgid "忍是勤中上　　能得涅槃處"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:858.2"
msgid "出家惱他人　　不名為沙門"
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:859.1"
msgid "此是毘<span class=\"t-gaiji\">鉢<!--gaiji,缽,1[金*本],2&#x9262;,3--> </span>尸如來應正等覺。說是戒經。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:860.1"
msgid "明眼避險途　　能至安隱處"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:860.2"
msgid "智者於生界　　能遠離諸惡"
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:861.1"
msgid "此是尸棄如來應正等覺。說是戒經。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:862.1"
msgid "不毀亦不害　　善護於戒經"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:862.2"
msgid "飲食知止足　　受用下臥具"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:862.3"
msgid "勤修增上定　　此是諸佛教"
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:863.1"
msgid "此是毘舍浮如來應正等覺。說是戒經。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="64"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:864.1"
msgid "譬如蜂採花　　不壞色與香"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:864.2"
msgid "但取其味去　　苾芻入聚然"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:864.3"
msgid "不違逆他人　　不觀作不作"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:864.4"
msgid "但自觀身行　　若正若不正"
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:865.1"
msgid "此是俱留孫如來應正等覺。說是戒經。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="65"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:866.1"
msgid "勿著於定心　　勤修寂靜處"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:866.2"
msgid "能救護無憂　　常令念不失"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:866.3"
msgid "若人能惠施　　福增怨自息"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:866.4"
msgid "修善除眾惡　　惑盡至涅槃"
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:867.1"
msgid "此是羯諾迦牟尼如來應正等覺。說是戒經。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:868.1"
msgid "一切惡莫作　　一切善應修"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:868.2"
msgid "遍調於自心　　是則諸佛教"
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:869.1"
msgid "此是迦攝波如來應正等覺。說是戒經。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="66"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:870.1"
msgid "護身為善哉　　能護語亦善"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:870.2"
msgid "護意為善哉　　盡護最為善"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:870.3"
msgid "苾芻護一切　　能解脫眾苦"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:870.4"
msgid "善護於口言　　亦善護於意"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:870.5"
msgid "身不作諸惡　　常淨三種業"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:870.6"
msgid "是則能隨順　　大仙所行道"
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:871.1"
msgid "此是釋迦如來應正等覺。說是戒經。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="67"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:872.1"
msgid "毘<span class=\"t-gaiji\">鉢<!--gaiji,缽,1[金*本],2&#x9262;,3--> </span>尸式棄　　毘舍俱留孫"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:872.2"
msgid "羯諾迦牟尼　　迦攝釋迦尊"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:872.3"
msgid "如是天中天　　無上調御者"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:872.4"
msgid "七佛皆雄猛　　能救護世間"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:872.5"
msgid "具足大名稱　　咸說此戒法"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:872.6"
msgid "諸佛及弟子　　咸共尊敬戒"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:872.7"
msgid "恭敬戒經故　　獲得無上果"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:872.8"
msgid "汝當求出離　　於佛教勤修"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:872.9"
msgid "降伏生死軍　　如象摧草舍"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:872.10"
msgid "於此法律中　　常為不放逸"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:872.11"
msgid "能竭煩惱海　　當盡苦邊際"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:872.12"
msgid "所為說戒經　　和合作長淨"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:872.13"
msgid "當共尊敬戒　　如<span class=\"t-gaiji\">犛<!--gaiji,犛,1[犛-未+牙],2&#x246C6;,3--> </span>牛愛尾"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:872.14"
msgid "我已說戒經　　眾僧長淨竟"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:872.15"
msgid "福利諸有情　　皆共成佛道"
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta"><span class="juanname">
msgctxt "lzh-mu-bi-pm:873.1"
msgid "根本說一切有部苾芻尼戒經"
msgstr ""

